21','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/253928876/s1920/dune-2021.webp/dune-2021.webp','Paul Atreides, a brilliant and gifted young man born into a great destiny beyond his understanding, must travel to the most dangerous planet in the\n universe to ensure the future of his family and his people. As malevolent forces explode into conflict over the planets exclusive supply of the most \n precious resource in existence-a commodity capable of unlocking humanitys greatest potential-only those who can conquer their fear will survive.'),('M18','Movie','Willy Wonka & the Chocolate Factory','85%','1h:39m','G','1971','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/247227511/s1920/willy-wonka-and-the-chocolate-factory.webp/willy-wonka-and-the-chocolate-factory.webp','When eccentric candy man Willy Wonka promises a lifetime supply of sweets and a tour of his chocolate factory to five lucky kids, penniless \n Charlie Bucket seeks the golden ticket that will make him a winner.'),('M19','Movie','The Devil Wears Prada','80%','1h:49m','PG-13','2006','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/304525006/s1920/the-devil-wears-prada.webp/the-devil-wears-prada.webp','Andy moves to New York to work in the fashion industry. Her boss is extremely demanding, cruel and wont let her succeed if she doesnt fit into\n the high class elegant look of their magazine'),('M2','Movie','The Shawshank Redemption','99%','2h:22m','R','1994','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/8652089/s1920/the-shawshank-redemption.webp/the-shawshank-redemption.webp','Framed in the 1940s for the double murder of his wife and her lover, upstanding banker Andy Dufresne begins a new life at the Shawshank prison,\n where he puts his accounting skills to work for an amoral warden. During his long stretch in prison, Dufresne comes to be admired by the other inmates\n -- including an older prisoner named Red -- for his integrity and unquenchable sense of hope.'),('M20','Movie','Legally Blonde','73%','1h:36m','PG-13','2001','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/265173610/s1920/legally-blonde.webp/legally-blonde.webp','Elle Woods, a fashionable sorority queen, is dumped by her boyfriend. She decides to follow him to law school, but while there, she figures out\n that there is more to herself than just looks.'),('M21','Movie','Coraline','87%','1h:40m','PG','2009','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/803378/s1920/coraline.webp/coraline.webp','A young girl discovers an idealized parallel universe behind a secret door in her new home, unaware that it contains a sinister secret.A young girl \n discovers an idealized parallel universe behind a secret door in her new home, unaware that it contains a sinister secret.'),('M22','Movie','Jumanji','78%','1h:44m','PG','1995','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/8655652/s1920/jumanji.webp/jumanji.webp','When siblings Judy and Peter discover an enchanted board game that opens the door to a magical world, they unwittingly invite Alan -- an adult whos\n been trapped inside the game for 26 years -- into their living room. Alans only hope for freedom is to finish the game, which proves risky as all three\n find themselves running from giant rhinoceroses, evil monkeys and other terrifying creatures.'),('M23','Movie','Night at the Museum','73%','1h:45m','PG','2006','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/271941308/s1920/night-at-the-museum.webp/night-at-the-museum.webp','Chaos reigns at the natural history museum when night watchman Larry Daley accidentally stirs up an ancient curse, awakening Attila the Hun, an army \n of gladiators, a Tyrannosaurus rex and other exhibits.'),('M24','Movie','Trick r Treat','76%','1h:22m','R','2007','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/176376560/s1920/trick-r-treat.webp/trick-r-treat.webp','Four interwoven stories that occur on Halloween: an everyday high school principal has a secret life as a serial killer; a college virgin might have\n just met the one guy for her; a group of teenagers pull a mean prank, and a bitter old recluse receives an uninvited guest.'),('M25','Movie','Friday the 13th','72%','1h:35m','R','1980','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/206842728/s1920/friday-the-13th-1980.webp/friday-the-13th-1980.webp','Camp counselors are stalked and murdered by an unknown assailant while trying to reopen a summer camp that was the site of a childs drowning.'),('M26','Movie','Sleeping Beauty','79%','1h:15m','G','1959','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/309252936/s1920/sleeping-beauty-1959.webp/sleeping-beauty-1959.webp','A beautiful princess born in a faraway kingdom is destined by a terrible curse to prick her finger on the spindle of a spinning wheel and fall into\n a deep sleep that can only be awakened by true loves first kiss. Determined to protect her, her parents ask three fairies to raise her in hiding. \n But the evil Maleficent is just as determined to seal the princesss fate.'),('M27','Movie','Curious George','71%','1h:29m','G','2006','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/243878286/s1920/curious-george.webp/curious-george.webp','When The Man in the Yellow Hat befriends Curious George in the jungle, they set off on a non-stop, fun-filled journey through the wonders of\n the big city toward the warmth of true friendship.'),('M28','Movie','The Polar Express','75%','1h:40m','G','2004','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/93113675/s1920/the-polar-express.webp/the-polar-express.webp','When a doubting young boy takes an extraordinary train ride to the North Pole, he embarks on a journey of self-discovery that shows him\n that the wonder of life never fades for those who believe.'),('M29','Movie','The Flash','77%','2h:24m','PG-13','2023','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/305800912/s1920/the-flash.webp/the-flash.webp','The speedster decides to use his superhuman pace to travel back in time and prevent his mother from dying. But his move has unexpected and\n chaotic consequences. The Flash finds himself stuck in a reality where the evil General Zod has re-emerged and no superheroes exist to challenge \n him. The Flash must rally with what allies he can find. Between a retired Batman, another Barry Allen, and a locked-up Supergirl, \n The Flash has friends, but does he have the time to save this world from certain destruction?'),('M3','Movie','The Perks of Being a Wallflower','86%','1h:43m','PG-13','2012','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/9634917/s1920/the-perks-of-being-a-wallflower.webp/the-perks-of-being-a-wallflower.webp','Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, 1991. High school freshman Charlie is a wallflower, always watching life from the sidelines, until two senior students,\n Sam and her stepbrother Patrick, become his mentors, helping him discover the joys of friendship, music and love.'),('M30','Movie','The Menu','80%','1h:48m','R','2022','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/302339489/s1920/the-menu-2022.webp/the-menu-2022.webp','Hawthorne is the epitome of high-class fine dining and exclusivity. The restaurant sits on an isolated coastal island and produces food that \n is also conceptual art. The chef at the head of Hawthorne is Slowik, whose staff are in obedient revelry of his genius. Margot and Tyler are a \n young couple who travel to the Hawthorne in order to experience something out of the ordinary. For Tyler, Hawthorne is a moving meditation on\n culinary culture but Margot is less enthused. As the evening unfolds, the experience becomes increasingly sinister and what starts as experimental\n cuisine takes on terrifying consequences for the dinner guests.'),('M31','Movie','Barbie','81%','1h:54m','PG-13','2023','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/306559353/s1920/barbie-2023.webp/barbie-2023.webp','When Barbie leaves Barbieland and finds herself in the real world, shes a fish out of water longing for her old life. Meanwhile, her boyfriend\n Ken seems at ease with the impossible standards of the human world. Can their relationship survive this clash of ideals?'),('M32','Movie','The Notebook','87%','1h:59m','PG-13','2004','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/115043902/s1920/the-notebook-2004.webp/the-notebook-2004.webp','An epic love story centered around an older man who reads aloud to a woman with Alzheimers. From a faded notebook, the old mans\n words bring to life the story about a couple who is separated by World War II, and is then passionately reunited, seven years later, after\n they have taken different paths'),('M33','Movie','Crazy, Stupid, Love','81%','1h:58m','PG-13','2011','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/28032185/s1920/crazy-stupid-love.webp/crazy-stupid-love.webp','Cal Weaver is living the American dream. He has a good job, a beautiful house, great children and a beautiful wife, named Emily. Cals seemingly\n perfect life unravels, however, when he learns that Emily has been unfaithful and wants a divorce. Over 40 and suddenly single, Cal is adrift in the fickle\n world of dating. Enter, Jacob Palmer, a self-styled player who takes Cal under his wing and teaches him how to be a hit with the ladies'),('M4','Movie','The Matrix Resurrections','69%','2h:28m','R','2021','Germany','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/257943910/s1920/the-matrix-resurrections.webp/the-matrix-resurrections.webp','Plagued by strange memories, Neos life takes an unexpected turn when he finds himself back inside the Matrix.'),('M5','Movie','Titanic','88%','3h:15m','PG-13','1997','United States','https://images.justwatch.com/backdrop/302953917/s1920/titanic-1997.webp/titanic-1997.webp','101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé.\n Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win t